title: WC14 - MOTD - Match Of The Day 15 1080i 27.06.2014
description:
WC14 - MOTD - Match Of The Day 15 27.06.2014 
Broadcast : BBC Two 
HD Presenter : Mark Chapman 
Video : MPEG-TS, 25 fps, 1920 x 1080, 6439 Kbps
Audio Track: English (AC-3, 48 KHz, 192 kbps) 
Credit : Sagopa Kajmer
 
Includes:

USA v Germany 
Portugal v Ghana
Algeria v Russia 
South Korea v Belgium.
 
Duration: 1 hour 

Mark Chapman presents highlights of the final matches in Group G as the USA play Germany and Portugal take on Ghana. There is also action from the games that decided the placings in Group H with Algeria facing Russia and South Korea meeting Belgium.
